title: Arri 16mm double system film printer
brief_description:
Arri 16mm double system film printer. Manufactured by Arnold & Richter Munchen. Model E-III/BT/U.
1 of 3: Printer
2 of 3: 1 x 2000’ magnetic coated film on core (in its original box)
3 of 3: Instruction manual
